Thermite.  You're probably thinking of thermite (a mixture of aluminum and 
iron oxide, interestingly enough).  Burns as several thousand degrees, makes 
it's own oxygen (so burns underwater, in a vacuum, etc).
It obviously doesn't leave a whole lot behind :-)

